QuestData.Title: With Friends Like You, Who Needs Anemones?
QuestData.Description:
I sometimes amuse myself with excursions into Zanj'ir Terrace, where the naga tough guys hang out.
I grab things that could be useful and stash them somewhere I can pick them up later.
I haven't been down there in a while.
I could have something in there you may find useful.
